"In vivo" imaging of atherosclerosis.

Gallino A(1), Stuber M, Crea F, Falk E, Corti R, Lekakis J, Schwitter J, Camici 
P, Gaemperli O, Di Valentino M, Prior J, Garcia-Garcia HM, Vlachopoulos C, 
